;;; All data coming form Harris' famous paper:
;;; "On the Use Of windows For Harmonic Analysis 
;;;  With The Discrete Fourier Transform"
;;; Proceedings of the IEEE, Vol. 66, No. 1 (pg. 51 to 84)
;;; January 1978

;;; Window coeffs. (a0, a1, a2, a3) 

